snippet.title: Let`s Play [PC]: Ara ngc 6397 (1998) [read description]
snippet.description:
Lets Play [PC]: Ara ngc 6397 
Complete walkthough except missing 4 minutes ... what is missing well when you press the right combination on the power box , turn off electricity , cut the wire , combine it with the battery you got from that TV and all this to  power a gun to kill a monkey so you can press a BUTTON AND SOMETHING AWESOME HAPPENS ... well now you can jump into that vent and  not get fried ....that`s all
